Package: sciColors
Type: Package
Title: Scientific Journal Color Palettes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jingyi", family = "Wang", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "jingyi@example.com"))
Description: A collection of 100 Hex color codes inspired by palettes commonly seen in Nature, Science, Cell, and other leading biology journals. Provides easy access to gradient and contrast color selections by theme.
